item.title: About Me
item.description: Hi, my name is Mateus Felipe Cumerlatto. I’m from Xanxerê-SC and I’m living in Joinville-SC, Brazil since the 6 years old. Currently, I’m working as a Data Engineer at Conta Azul. About studies, i have bachelor’s degree in Software Enginering from Universidade da Região de Joinville. Interested in structures and pipelines of data, python, spark/pyspark, data infrastructure engineering, cloud computing, AWS and Terraform. I want still focus in open-source projects with personal projects and contributions.
